ğŸ§° Technologies

Python (Pandas, NumPy, Scikit-learn)

GeoPandas, Folium, Plotly for visualization

Streamlit or Dash for web interface

Matplotlib / Seaborn for analytics and plots

âš™ï¸ Setup & Execution

Clone the repository:

git clone https://github.com/yourusername/USCities-HousePrices.git
cd USCities-HousePrices


